{"tid":1456091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去留自決！天佑香港！","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:46:46.000Z","uid":27534,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e356a6e8d8d9d14883d13e4b595e4795769ff849","tid":1456091,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"而家機場情況係有啲唔對路，呢個係事實<br />\n- 停網<br />\n- 停機<br />\n- 停飛<br />\n- 有煙彈<br />\n- 有通告<br />\n- 機場死位<br />\n- 難走難救<br />\n<br />\n但都係一句，去留自決<br />\n其他人唔會指指點點<br />\n決定留喺現場嘅手足<br />\n一定要做好準備<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會割，核彈都唔割！<br />\n<br />\n你永遠唔知自己既選擇是對是錯，大家要相信在場的手足嘅決定！<br />\n<br />\n係呢個人心惶惶嘅時候，我知道一定好多無入機場嘅人會擔心，但都請你地忍一忍，唔好係依個時候瘋狂msg/打電話去，講一句萬事小心已夠好足夠<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港！"},{"pid":"b348af50483543549c60d62bcfa3eaeddb0bb076","tid":1456091,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"自推自推自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafcdadd7887ce7d1bded33f40adda07cf1d678a","tid":1456091,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"自推自推自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2604ba7c0b695f27531e093da26f34ecf7f9c54a","tid":1456091,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:45:40.000Z","msg":"自推自推自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43bf2ce86fa1e1e90c771033af57adbd4cc6d820","tid":1456091,"uid":27534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"自推自推自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}